{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-18",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_18_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "The Fall Guy",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 6,
  "page_total": 8,
  "page_start_sec": 1231.86,
  "page_end_sec": 1479.5,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.553,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 1231.86,
      "end": 1232.3,
      "text": "Now,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1232.32,
      "end": 1232.54,
      "text": "now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1232.6,
      "end": 1233.04,
      "text": "Wilmer,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1233.2,
      "end": 1233.7,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 1233.98,
      "end": 1235.34,
      "text": "we can't have any of that."
    },
    {
      "start": 1236.16,
      "end": 1238.84,
      "text": "You shouldn't let yourself attach so much importance to these",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1238.96,
      "end": 1239.12,
      "text": "things."
    },
    {
      "start": 1239.5,
      "end": 1240.1,
      "text": "You..."
    },
    {
      "start": 1240.84,
      "end": 1241.18,
      "text": "The boy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1241.32,
      "end": 1243.02,
      "text": "not taking his eyes from Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1243.12,
      "end": 1245.36,
      "text": "spoke in a choked voice out the side of"
    },
    {
      "start": 1245.36,
      "end": 1245.76,
      "text": "his mouth."
    },
    {
      "start": 1246.688,
      "end": 1248.3,
      "text": "Make him lay off me then.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1249.66,
      "end": 1252.0,
      "text": "I'm going to fog him if he keeps it up,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1252.1,
      "end": 1252.9,
      "text": "and there won't be"
    },
    {
      "start": 1253.0,
      "end": 1254.96,
      "text": "anything that'll stop me from doing it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1255.5,
      "end": 1256.06,
      "text": "Now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1256.06,
      "end": 1256.62,
      "text": "Wilmer,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1256.84,
      "end": 1258.78,
      "text": "Gutman said and turned to Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 1259.44,
      "end": 1259.84,
      "text": "His face",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1260.04,
      "end": 1261.7,
      "text": "and voice were under control now."
    },
    {
      "start": 1262.6,
      "end": 1263.36,
      "text": "Your plan is,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1263.46,
      "end": 1263.9,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1264.14,
      "end": 1265.6,
      "text": "as I said in the first place,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1265.82,
      "end": 1266.52,
      "text": "not at all"
    },
    {
      "start": 1266.58,
      "end": 1266.92,
      "text": "practical."
    },
    {
      "start": 1267.33,
      "end": 1269.8,
      "text": "Let's not say anything more about it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1270.72,
      "end": 1272.54,
      "text": "Spade looked from one of them to the other.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1273.02,
      "end": 1274.06,
      "text": "He had stopped smiling."
    },
    {
      "start": 1274.78,
      "end": 1276.6,
      "text": "His face held no expression at all.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1276.86,
      "end": 1278.52,
      "text": "I say what I please,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1278.84,
      "end": 1279.58,
      "text": "he told them."
    },
    {
      "start": 1280.32,
      "end": 1281.14,
      "text": "You certainly do,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1281.36,
      "end": 1282.26,
      "text": "Gutman said quickly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1282.82,
      "end": 1285.42,
      "text": "and that's one of the things I've always admired in you.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1285.86,
      "end": 1287.18,
      "text": "But this matter is,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1287.34,
      "end": 1287.96,
      "text": "as I say,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1288.12,
      "end": 1289.24,
      "text": "not at all practical,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1289.88,
      "end": 1293.46,
      "text": "so there's not the least bit of use of discussing it any further,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1293.62,
      "end": 1295.06,
      "text": "as you can see for yourself."
    },
    {
      "start": 1295.81,
      "end": 1297.44,
      "text": "I can't see it for myself,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1297.72,
      "end": 1298.26,
      "text": "Spade said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1298.66,
      "end": 1300.14,
      "text": "and you haven't made me see it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1300.2,
      "end": 1301.5,
      "text": "and I don't think you can."
    },
    {
      "start": 1302.36,
      "end": 1303.34,
      "text": "He frowned at Gutman.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1304.288,
      "end": 1305.12,
      "text": "Let's get this straight.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1306.02,
      "end": 1308.14,
      "text": "Am I wasting time talking to you?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1308.5,
      "end": 1310.18,
      "text": "I thought this was your show."
    },
    {
      "start": 1311.14,
      "end": 1312.66,
      "text": "Should I do my talking to the punk?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1313.5,
      "end": 1314.56,
      "text": "I know how to do that.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1315.74,
      "end": 1318.14,
      "text": "no sir gutman replied you're quite right",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1318.14,
      "end": 1321.42,
      "text": "in dealing with me spade said all right"
    },
    {
      "start": 1322.14,
      "end": 1322.68,
      "text": "now i've",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1322.68,
      "end": 1325.28,
      "text": "got another suggestion it's not as good as the"
    },
    {
      "start": 1325.28,
      "end": 1328.06,
      "text": "first but it's better than nothing want to hear"
    },
    {
      "start": 1328.22,
      "end": 1328.4,
      "text": "it"
    },
    {
      "start": 1329.18,
      "end": 1330.1,
      "text": "most assuredly",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1330.84,
      "end": 1333.82,
      "text": "give them cairo cairo hastily picked",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1333.82,
      "end": 1335.72,
      "text": "up his pistol from the table beside him"
    },
    {
      "start": 1335.87,
      "end": 1339.03,
      "text": "he held it tight in his lap with both hands its"
    },
    {
      "start": 1339.3,
      "end": 1341.8,
      "text": "muzzle pointed at the floor a little to one side"
    },
    {
      "start": 1342.02,
      "end": 1342.34,
      "text": "of the sofa."
    },
    {
      "start": 1342.7,
      "end": 1345.14,
      "text": "His face had become yellowish again."
    },
    {
      "start": 1345.6,
      "end": 1348.7,
      "text": "His black eyes darted their gaze from face to"
    },
    {
      "start": 1348.7,
      "end": 1348.98,
      "text": "face."
    },
    {
      "start": 1349.8,
      "end": 1352.06,
      "text": "The opaqueness of his eyes made them seem flat,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1352.26,
      "end": 1352.84,
      "text": "two-dimensional."
    },
    {
      "start": 1353.57,
      "end": 1354.22,
      "text": "Gutman,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1354.38,
      "end": 1355.18,
      "text": "looking as if he"
    },
    {
      "start": 1355.18,
      "end": 1357.38,
      "text": "could not believe he had heard what he had heard,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1357.52,
      "end": 1358.08,
      "text": "asked,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1358.66,
      "end": 1359.14,
      "text": "Do what?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1360.12,
      "end": 1361.26,
      "text": "Give the police Cairo.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1361.48,
      "end": 1361.58,
      "text": "Gutman"
    },
    {
      "start": 1362.56,
      "end": 1363.78,
      "text": "seemed about to laugh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1364.0,
      "end": 1364.82,
      "text": "but he did not laugh."
    },
    {
      "start": 1365.1,
      "end": 1365.88,
      "text": "Finally,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1365.9,
      "end": 1366.76,
      "text": "he exclaimed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1366.9,
      "end": 1367.48,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1367.54,
      "end": 1368.0,
      "text": "baguette,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1368.08,
      "end": 1368.34,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1368.76,
      "end": 1369.9,
      "text": "in an uncertain tone."
    },
    {
      "start": 1370.84,
      "end": 1372.42,
      "text": "It's not as good as giving them the punk,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1372.92,
      "end": 1373.26,
      "text": "Spade said."
    },
    {
      "start": 1374.112,
      "end": 1375.06,
      "text": "Cairo's not a gunman",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1375.06,
      "end": 1378.36,
      "text": "and he carries a smaller gun than Thursby and Jacoby were shot with."
    },
    {
      "start": 1379.28,
      "end": 1380.08,
      "text": "We'll have to go to more",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1380.16,
      "end": 1381.1,
      "text": "trouble framing him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1381.64,
      "end": 1383.64,
      "text": "but that's better than not giving the police anybody."
    },
    {
      "start": 1384.8,
      "end": 1385.88,
      "text": "Cairo cried in a voice",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1385.98,
      "end": 1386.98,
      "text": "shrill with indignation."
    },
    {
      "start": 1387.872,
      "end": 1388.86,
      "text": "Suppose we give them you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1389.0,
      "end": 1389.26,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 1389.32,
      "end": 1389.72,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1389.76,
      "end": 1390.75,
      "text": "or Miss O'Shaughnessy."
    },
    {
      "start": 1391.56,
      "end": 1392.2,
      "text": "How about that",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1392.32,
      "end": 1394.24,
      "text": "if you're so set on giving them somebody?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1395.424,
      "end": 1398.08,
      "text": "Spade smiled at the Levantine and answered him evenly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1398.63,
      "end": 1401.6,
      "text": "you people want the falcon i've got it"
    },
    {
      "start": 1402.18,
      "end": 1405.28,
      "text": "a fall guy is part of the price i'm asking as for miss",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1405.46,
      "end": 1405.86,
      "text": "o'shaughnessy"
    },
    {
      "start": 1406.8,
      "end": 1408.94,
      "text": "his dispassionate glance moved to her",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1408.95,
      "end": 1411.3,
      "text": "white perplexed face and then back to cairo"
    },
    {
      "start": 1411.46,
      "end": 1414.3,
      "text": "and his shoulders rose and fell a fraction of an inch"
    },
    {
      "start": 1415.12,
      "end": 1417.06,
      "text": "if you think she can be rigged for the part",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1417.26,
      "end": 1419.5,
      "text": "i'm perfectly willing to discuss it with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 1420.34,
      "end": 1422.96,
      "text": "the girl put her hands to her throat uttered a short",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1423.3,
      "end": 1425.5,
      "text": "strangled cry and moved farther away from him."
    },
    {
      "start": 1425.92,
      "end": 1426.8,
      "text": "Cairo,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1426.94,
      "end": 1428.88,
      "text": "his face and body twitching with excitement,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1429.34,
      "end": 1429.78,
      "text": "exclaimed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1429.95,
      "end": 1432.12,
      "text": "You seem to forget that you are not"
    },
    {
      "start": 1432.12,
      "end": 1433.9,
      "text": "in a position to insist on anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 1434.944,
      "end": 1436.0,
      "text": "Spade laughed a harsh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1436.12,
      "end": 1436.98,
      "text": "derisive snort."
    },
    {
      "start": 1438.048,
      "end": 1440.48,
      "text": "Gutman said in a voice that tried to make firmness",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1440.71,
      "end": 1441.46,
      "text": "ingratiating,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1442.24,
      "end": 1442.58,
      "text": "Come now,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1442.62,
      "end": 1442.92,
      "text": "gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1443.1,
      "end": 1445.42,
      "text": "let's keep our discussion on a friendly basis."
    },
    {
      "start": 1446.56,
      "end": 1447.6,
      "text": "But there certainly is,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1447.72,
      "end": 1449.22,
      "text": "he was addressing Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1449.41,
      "end": 1450.76,
      "text": "something in what Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 1450.84,
      "end": 1451.44,
      "text": "Cairo says."
    },
    {
      "start": 1452.32,
      "end": 1454.16,
      "text": "you must take into consideration the",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1455.08,
      "end": 1458.64,
      "text": "like hell i must spade flung his words out with a brutal",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1458.74,
      "end": 1461.16,
      "text": "sort of carelessness that gave them more weight"
    },
    {
      "start": 1461.64,
      "end": 1463.93,
      "text": "than they could have got from a dramatic emphasis"
    },
    {
      "start": 1464.3,
      "end": 1468.82,
      "text": "or from loudness if you kill me how are you going to get the bird"
    },
    {
      "start": 1470.14,
      "end": 1471.72,
      "text": "if i know you can't afford to kill",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1471.72,
      "end": 1474.58,
      "text": "me till you have it how are you going to scare me"
    },
    {
      "start": 1474.58,
      "end": 1477.92,
      "text": "into giving it to you gutman cocked his head to"
    },
    {
      "start": 1478.02,
      "end": 1479.5,
      "text": "the left and considered these questions."
    }
  ]
}